65010/idi-kembali-laporkan-tiga-dokter-meninggal-terkait-virus-corona|title=IDI Kembali Laporkan Tiga Dokter Meninggal Terkait Virus Corona|last=Mahardhika|first=Muhammad Anjar|website=detikHealth|language=id|access-date=2020-04-04}}</ref>\n|COVID-19 (+)\n|\n|-\n|23\n|3 April 2020\n|4 April 2020\n|Medistra Hospital, Jakarta\n|dr Ketty Herawati Sultana<ref name=\":9\" />\n|COVID-19 (+)\n|\n|-\n|24\n|3 April 2020\n|4 April 2020\n|Persahabatan Central General Hospital, Jakarta\n|Dr dr Lukman Shebubakar SpOT, PhD<ref name=\":9\" />\n|COVID-19 (+)\n|Orthopedic Doctor at Premier Bintaro Hospital\n|-\n|25\n|4 April 2020\n|5 April 2020\n|Siloam Hospital Sepanjang Jaya, Rawalumbu, Bekasi\n|Lukman Nulhakim<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.detik.com/berita/d-4965517/kabar-duka-ini-jejak-camat-bekasi-utara-meninggal-gegara-positif-corona|title=Kabar Duka! Ini Jejak Camat Bekasi Utara Meninggal Gegara Positif Corona|last=detikcom|first=Tim|website=detiknews|language=id-ID|access-date=2020-04-04}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://bekasimedia.com/2020/04/04/camat-bekasi-utara-dimakamkan-dengan-prosedur-covid-19/|title=Camat Bekasi Utara dimakamkan dengan Prosedur Covid-19|last=bekasimedia|date=2020-04-04|website=BEKASIMEDIA.COM|language=id-ID|access-date=2020-04-04}}</ref>\n|COVID-19 (+)\n|North Bekasi Head\n|-\n|26\n|\n|5 April 2020\n|\n|drg Umi Susana Widjaja, SpPM<ref name=\":10\">{{Cite web|url=https://health.detik.com/berita-detikhealth/d-4965649/17-dokter-dan-5-dokter-gigi-meninggal-selama-pandemi-corona-ini-daftarnya|title=17 Dokter dan 5 Dokter Gigi Meninggal Selama Pandemi Corona, Ini Daftarnya|last=Pramudiarja|first=AN Uyung|website=detikHealth|language=id|access-date=2020-04-05}}</ref>\n|COVID-19 (+)\n|\n|-\n|27\n|\n|5 April 2020\n|\n|drg Yuniarto Budi Santoso, MKM<ref name=\":10\" />\n|COVID-19 (+)\n|\n|-\n|28\n|\n|5 April 2020\n|\n|drg Amutabia P Artsianti, SpOrt<ref name=\":10\" />\n|COVID-19 (+)\n|\n|-\n|29\n|\n|5 April 2020\n|\n|drg Roselani Widajati Orang, SpProst<